---
title: Manage
---

## Access Manage

- From MAS Admin link, you can select Manage application from the AppSwitcher (9 dots icon) or the click obn gear icon in the navigation bar.
  ![image](images/appswitcher.png)

- You can also get the Manage link from the OpenShift console.
![image](images/routes.png)

- You can use `ui` bundle or `all` bundle location link. Append `/maximo` to access Manage.
- You can go to Maximo Application Suite by clicking `Maximo Application Suite` on the header on top right corner.

![image](images/manage.png)

## Troubleshooting
- Check [logs](logging) for errors.
